{"id": "otel-ma-001", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "medium", "query": "OTEL 面板显示 frontend 服务的 trace error rate 突然从 0.5% 涨到 8%，同时 Prometheus 显示 http_server_duration p95 翻倍。让 metrics agent 和 troubleshoot agent 协作分析，给出联合结论。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "troubleshoot"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": ["p95", "error_rate"], "expected_entities": ["frontend", "prometheus"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces", "args_contains": {"service": "frontend"}}, {"tool": "query_metrics", "args_contains": {"query": "http_server_duration"}}], "expected_answer_contains": ["metrics agent", "troubleshoot agent", "error_rate", "p95", "collaboration"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-002", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "hard", "query": "大规模故障场景：多个服务同时报警 —— frontend LCP p95 到 8s、checkout error rate 15%、adservice gRPC 超时、cart service 返回 500。启动全部三个子 agent（metrics、troubleshoot、audit）做联合根因分析，最终由 supervisor 合成一份统一报告。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "troubleshoot", "audit-sop"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": ["p95", "lcp", "error_rate"], "expected_entities": ["frontend", "checkout", "adservice", "cart"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces"}, {"tool": "query_metrics"}], "expected_answer_contains": ["supervisor", "synthesize", "multi-agent", "root cause", "frontend", "checkout", "adservice", "cart"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-003", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "medium", "query": "先执行 Prometheus 指标检查发现 recommendation 服务的 RPS 突增 300%，然后 troubleshoot agent 从 Jaeger trace 中定位到是某个用户在循环调用推荐接口。请按这个协作模式输出分析报告。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "troubleshoot"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": ["rps"], "expected_entities": ["recommendation", "jaeger", "prometheus"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces", "args_contains": {"service": "recommendation"}}, {"tool": "query_metrics", "args_contains": {"query": "rate("}}], "expected_answer_contains": ["troubleshoot", "RPS", "trace", "recommendation", "loop"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-004", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "hard", "query": "audit agent 需要审计所有服务的 SLA 合规情况，请 metrics agent 提供过去 24h 的 OTEL 指标数据（可用性、延迟、错误预算），然后 audit agent 输出合规评分和不合规项清单。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "audit-sop"], "expected_intent": "audit", "expected_metrics": ["slo", "error_budget"], "expected_entities": ["sla", "compliance"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_metrics"}], "expected_answer_contains": ["audit", "metrics", "SLA", "compliance", "error budget", "24h", "score"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-005", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "medium", "query": "supervisor 发现用户问题涉及 OTEL trace 和 metric 的交叉分析，请规划子 agent 分工：metrics agent 负责 Prometheus 指标异常检测，troubleshoot agent 负责 Jaeger trace 根因定位，audit agent 负责评估变更风险。输出协作计划。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "troubleshoot", "audit-sop"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": [], "expected_entities": ["supervisor", "plan"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces"}, {"tool": "query_metrics"}], "expected_answer_contains": ["supervisor", "plan", "metrics agent", "troubleshoot agent", "audit agent", "delegation"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-006", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "medium", "query": "从 OTEL metrics 中发现过去 6 小时 token 消耗增长了 40%，内存使用也上升了 25%。请 metrics agent 量化趋势，audit agent 做成本影响评估并给出优化建议。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "audit-sop"], "expected_intent": "audit", "expected_metrics": [], "expected_entities": ["token", "memory", "cost"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_metrics"}], "expected_answer_contains": ["token", "memory", "cost", "optimization", "trend", "metrics agent", "audit agent"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-007", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "hard", "query": "Jaeger trace 显示 /api/orders/detail 接口有一个 5s 的慢调用链路，穿过 4 个微服务。请 troubleshoot agent 从 trace 中提取每个 span 的耗时，metrics agent 验证对应时间段的 DB 连接池和 Redis 命中率，一起定位根因。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "troubleshoot"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": [], "expected_entities": ["orders", "db", "redis", "jaeger"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces", "args_contains": {"service": "orders"}}, {"tool": "query_metrics", "args_contains": {"query": "redis"}}], "expected_answer_contains": ["span", "waterfall", "DB", "Redis", "bottleneck", "collaboration", "5s"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-008", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "hard", "query": "闭环排障场景：执行巡检规则（LCP > 4000ms、error rate > 5%、Redis hit rate < 90%），发现 3 项失败；troubleshoot agent 从 Jaeger trace 和 Prometheus metrics 做根因分析；audit agent 评估修复方案的 SLA 风险。三个 agent 协作输出完整的闭环报告。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "troubleshoot", "audit-sop"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": ["lcp", "error_rate"], "expected_entities": ["redis", "sla"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces"}, {"tool": "query_metrics"}], "expected_answer_contains": ["troubleshoot", "audit", "根因", "SLA", "closed-loop"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-009", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "medium", "query": "业务团队想定义「下单成功率」和「支付转化率」两个 OTEL 业务指标。请 metrics agent 设计 PromQL 和采集方案（numerator/denominator/去重），audit agent 评估数据质量和合规风险。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "audit-sop"], "expected_intent": "metrics", "expected_metrics": [], "expected_entities": ["conversion", "order", "payment"], "expected_tool_calls": [], "expected_answer_contains": ["numerator", "denominator", "dedupe", "conversion", "compliance", "PromQL", "business metric"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-010", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "hard", "query": "发布验证场景：release-2026.07.05 刚上线，请全部三个子 agent 并行工作 —— metrics agent 对比发布前后 Prometheus 指标（LCP、error_rate、throughput），troubleshoot agent 分析 Jaeger trace 中的异常 span，audit agent 评估发布合规性。supervisor 合成发布验证结论和回滚建议。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "troubleshoot", "audit-sop"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": ["lcp", "error_rate", "throughput"], "expected_entities": ["release", "deploy"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces"}, {"tool": "query_metrics"}], "expected_answer_contains": ["release", "verification", "before", "after", "rollback", "agents", "synthesize"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-011", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "easy", "query": "先让 metrics agent 从 Prometheus 查一下当前所有服务的 HTTP 请求量 Top 5，然后 troubleshoot agent 对排名第一的服务做 trace 分析，看看有没有异常。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "troubleshoot"], "expected_intent": "metrics", "expected_metrics": ["throughput"], "expected_entities": ["prometheus"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_metrics"}, {"tool": "query_traces"}], "expected_answer_contains": ["top 5", "throughput", "trace", "metrics agent", "troubleshoot agent"]}
{"id": "otel-ma-012", "category": "otel_multi_agent", "difficulty": "medium", "query": "从 Jaeger trace 中检测到 adservice 和 cart service 之间有循环调用（retry chain），每次重试耗时约 200ms。请 troubleshoot agent 分析 trace 链路，metrics agent 统计 retry rate 趋势，audit agent 给出 SLA 影响评估。", "expected_skills": ["otel-query", "troubleshoot", "audit-sop"], "expected_intent": "troubleshoot", "expected_metrics": ["retry_rate"], "expected_entities": ["adservice", "cart", "retry", "jaeger"], "expected_tool_calls": [{"tool": "query_traces", "args_contains": {"min_duration_ms": 200}}, {"tool": "query_metrics", "args_contains": {"query": "retry"}}], "expected_answer_contains": ["retry chain", "adservice", "cart", "SLA", "trace", "trend"]}
